{"tid":1762542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"寶福山 周同學","createTime":"2019-11-29T16:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T16:35:02.000Z","uid":324071,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"02839dcae1afb17c0ce26076dbaae2eaf1103ab7","tid":1762542,"uid":324071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:10:05.000Z","msg":"你話我左膠好,風向撚又好,五毛都好<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真係唔好直接搞殯儀館</span><br />\n周同學走左 佢地仲要趕盡殺絕 令梓樂冇得安息<br />\n的確係人神共憤,論罪當誅<br />\n不過<br />\n其他先人呢？佢地唔關事㗎<br />\n革命無可避免地係會有犧牲<br />\n但係要已逝者咁樣犧牲 被打擾係應該，合理同可接受既咩?<br />\n大家唔好因為呢股怒火而有種唯我獨尊既諗法,<br />\n為左幫梓樂報仇而漠視其他先人<br />\n克制先可以贏得支持<br />\n裝修殯儀館真係會有好多人支持?<br />\n<br />\n係咪一定要裝修先可以達成目的<br />\n會唔會佢有其他業務可以代而裝修<br />\n避免直接觸動到較忌諱既事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位手足可唔可以停一停 諗一諗 三思<br />\n要顧及大局<br />\n我唔係當梓樂係condom<br />\n而係相信我地會有更好既方法去處理<br />\n除左鬥力之外更需鬥智<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2f235902268b6900002f93f541ed792987c005","tid":1762542,"uid":324071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:16:36.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"4914133aa4ee59b6e1869533bf949a105bb07e84","tid":1762542,"uid":324071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:16:50.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"d6c39bfe87d012c836f80db2880dfc9c3b8a2396","tid":1762542,"uid":324071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:17:00.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"3081539f4f7059f2f718b6e21dfb8e0058d43eca","tid":1762542,"uid":324071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:17:11.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"},{"pid":"85a05891099e2e5cd5b9165efe506ccd8b12e287","tid":1762542,"uid":324071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:17:25.000Z","msg":"自推5/10"},{"pid":"465585d1fe35044f6c0bc9831c827c5634173f3f","tid":1762542,"uid":324071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:17:37.000Z","msg":"自推6/10"},{"pid":"1ca2c7c82a1be